          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Counseling for Career Choice Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to award competitive grants to state educational agencies and, through them, subgrants to eligible entities (e.g., local educational agencies) to implement comprehensive school career counseling programs.</p>]]>
